      "content": "i know about the hotlines but it doesn't change anything. it's not like a temporary crisis... it's just how things are now. everything is just empty. it feels like the person i was is actually dead, and i'm just stuck wandering around in this shell. it feels so much more real than any \"help\" could ever be. it's just... heavy. so heavy.",
